:<font size="15">לילה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
לילה    ליל    ליל / layil  lêyl  layelâh / lah'-yil, lale, lah'-yel-aw

===Etymology===
From the same as [[לוּל]]  {{HH|3883}}; 

===Noun===
'''לילה'''

# Properly a twist (away of the light), that is, night; figuratively adversity: - ([mid-]) [[night]] (season).

